  <title><literal>ReadExten()</literal></title>

  <indexterm significance="preferred">
    <primary>Dialplan-Applikationen</primary>

    <secondary><code>ReadExten()</code></secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <simpara>Read DTMF extension.</simpara>

  <synopsis>ReadExten(<replaceable>variable</replaceable>[,<replaceable>prompt_filename</replaceable>[,<replaceable>context</replaceable>[,<replaceable>option</replaceable>[,<replaceable>timeout</replaceable>]]]])</synopsis>

  <simpara>Prompts the caller to input an extension, listens for DTMF and
  stores the entered digits in the specified variable.</simpara>

